text:
I recently sprained my ankle during workout, thankfully there is a xray machine to determine the seriousness of my injury.

The whole process is very smooth, from the booking, to nurse facilitating and doctor’s diagnosis
Went to visit the doctor for my busted toe. He was very professional and gentle on my wound. Explained the choices that I have and his best recommendation.
My daughter recommended this clinic for health screening. Was indeed very satisfied with the service of the staff and doctor knowledge. Highly recommend!

The staff are very friendly and welcoming from the moment I arrived. The doctor took the time to explain my condition clearly and made sure all my questions were answered. I had a pleasant visit. Will recommend to my family & friends.
Did my health screening here—great service and friendly staff. Everything was smooth and well-organized. Highly recommend!
